# Agent workspace (absolute path outside repo - git will never track it)
# NOTE: ~/.tetora/workspace/ is an absolute path, no .gitignore entry needed.
# Git does not expand ~ in patterns, and absolute paths outside the repo
# are naturally ignored. This comment documents the workspace location.

